4, 802.1, 186.2, 813.5]}, {"text": "maintained for 28 days in the induction medium with medium changes every 48 h. The cells", "bbox": [252.5, 831.7, 711.9, 845.6]}, {"text": "were then stained with Oil Red O (Sigma). Briefly, the cells were first fixed with 4% paraformal-", "bbox": [252.5, 848.1, 727.2, 862.0]}, {"text": "dehyde for 10 min and then with 60% isopropanol for 5 min after rinsing with PBS. They were", "bbox": [252.5, 864.5, 722.8, 878.4]}, {"text": "then stained with Oil Red O for 5 min, rinsed with distilled water until the water was clear and", "bbox": [252.5, 880.9, 721.9, 894.9]}, {"text": "PLOS ONE | DOI:10.1371/journal.pone.0127992 June 10, 2015 6 / 25", "bbox": [45.5, 945.2, 727.3, 956.7]}]}